WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.371
To set up the class, you import trainees from an Excel file.

00:00:04.371 --> 00:00:07.576
Before saving, the platform shows a preview:

00:00:07.576 --> 00:00:11.729
each row appears valid or in red, with the error flagged.

00:00:11.729 --> 00:00:14.060
Only the valid ones are created.
